  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Cosy Rooms without a view</strong> are around 26m<sup>2</sup>, sleeping two people in a double bed, and a bathroom with a bath tub with shower. These rooms are have a quiet location at the back of the hotel, with no view, they are less exposed to the sun and overlook a wall. </p>
<p><strong>Alpine Rooms</strong> are around 29m<sup>2</sup> sleeping two people in a double bed. These rooms have a balcony with a lovely mountain view, and a bathroom with a bath tub and a separate shower.</p>
<p>Beds can be made up as twin beds or a double bed. Please specify your preference at the time of booking. Both rooms can accommodate a cot or a third person in a single put up bed (up to 16 years of age) on request.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Satellite TV</span></li>
<li><span>Wi-Fi</span></li>
<li><span>Tea and coffee facilities</span></li>
<li><span>Most rooms have a balcony</span></li>
<li>Bath with showerhead attachment </li>
<li>WC </li>
<li>Bathrobes and slippers </li>
<li>Toiletries </li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
